# SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT OR Apache-2.0
#
# The production image (Dockerfile) ONLY copies the prebuilt static binary staged
# under dist/<arch>/ironcache. Nothing else from the repo belongs in the build
# context, so this ignores everything except the dist/ staging tree. A tight
# context keeps `docker build` fast and prevents leaking source / secrets into a
# build layer.

# Ignore everything by default...
*

# ...then re-include only the dist/ staging tree the Dockerfile copies from.
!dist/
!dist/**

# Belt-and-suspenders: never include these even if a future Dockerfile widens the
# context.
.git
.github
target
crates
docs
scripts
bench-results
deploy
**/*.rs
**/*.toml
**/.DS_Store
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
